[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Cleans up the weather overlay. Fog is removed by default; wind and rain stay unless you turn them off too.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]Fog off[/b] — removes indoor and outdoor fog. The effect applies to all zones including dungeons where the fog was densest. Performance also improves slightly because the fog overlay is disabled, not just hidden.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Optional wind off[/b] — separate toggle. Keeps the air completely still. Off by default (vanilla keeps wind).[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Optional rain off[/b] — separate toggle. Suppresses rain events entirely. Off by default.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Live toggle[/b] — changes apply the moment you tick or untick them in the config. No restart, no reload.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Cutscene-aware[/b] — weather effects you disabled stay disabled even through scripted weather moments (sermons, special events).[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/55]Misc. Bits and Bobs[/url] — includes "Remove Cinematic Letterboxing" and "Lessen Footprint Impact". Pairs with Fog Be Gone for a cleaner visual presentation overall.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/81]Show Me Moar[/url] — resolution, zoom, and HUD scaling control.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/125]Rest In Patches[/url] — small vanilla bug fixes including player-movement judder and footprint fade-out.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/79]Graveyard Keeper BepInEx 5 Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/79][size=3]Graveyard Keeper BepInEx 5 Pack at Graveyard Keeper Nexus - Mods and community (nexusmods.com)[/size][/url]
[/list]
[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...&#92;steamapps&#92;common&#92;Graveyard Keeper&#92;BepInEx[/code][/size]

